<h1>Stage One Instructions</h1>

<p>In this stage, you get £1 in vouchers. The other pupil gets £0. You can give 
them some, none or all of your vouchers, in multiples of 10p. Whatever vouchers you
do not give to the other pupil, you can keep.</p>

<p>Remember, if the computer picks you, your choice will decide how much
you and the other pupil get from this stage.</p>

<p>You have to choose how much you will give the other pupil.</p>

